Sentry
A sly one wants to help an old mage. He knows that there is a guard who has let the mage through to the mine on more than one occasion. You have to meet the sentry, so leave him a note near the guard room.
#subobj 1
Go to the guard post
The guard post is located next to the gate to the mine.
#subobj 2
Leave a note
You can put the letter to the sentry in the chest next to the post.